Before we continue, please make sure that all of the software <BR> 
on your system is up to date. If you're on arch, you can do this <BR>
by issuing the following at the command prompt: <BR> <BR>
sudo pacman -Syu <BR> <BR>
If using Ubuntu, then you can do: <BR> <BR>
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade <BR><BR>
Is your system up to date?
